stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Monitoring
    Monitoring --> ExceptionDetected : anomaly detected
    ExceptionDetected --> Classification : log captured
    Classification --> LLMAnalysis : exception type unknown
    Classification --> AgentDispatch : exception type known
    LLMAnalysis --> AgentDispatch : remediation plan generated
    AgentDispatch --> Recovery : agent executed fix
    Recovery --> Verification : fix applied
    Verification --> Resolved : health checks pass
    Verification --> Escalation : checks fail
    Escalation --> Failed : manual intervention required
    Resolved --> [*]
    Failed --> [*]